About the product
  • FOREHEAD AND EAR MODE: Free to switch the detection mode from Forehead to Ear which is the easiest and most practical way to take temperature.
  • CLINICAL ACCURACY and RELIABILITY: Equipped with the most advanced medical infrared technology for accuracy and reliability. Recommended by medical experts following its vigorous FDA clinical tests to confirm its consistency and reliability.
  • RELIABLE AND READINGS STORE: Thermometer can store and recall up to 20 readings for baby and adults, available to help you track the trend of body temperature.
  • FAST AND ACCURATE READINGS: With 2 buttons Head and Ear,provides fast clinical accurate instant temperature within 1 second and precise reading. A loud beep will notify you it is done.
  • MONEY BACK GUARANTEE AND WARRANTY: Our top priority is your satisfaction. We still offer a 30-day 100% Hassle free money back guarantee. In addition to this you are covered by the 1 year manufacturer’s guarantee.

All Product Information Customer Q&A's Customer Reviews

Product description

The Product Features of FDA Thermometer
1. Dual mode use(Forehead or ear detection)
2. 1 second measurement time
3. Fever warning
4. 20 readings memory recall

How to get accurate reading temperature?
1.Make sure the position of the measurement is correct, don’t measure the place which is near to eyebrows ,just test forehead , only that’s correct position.
2.Please don’t press the forehead or drill into the ear hole for long time(more than 5s) to measure multiple temp ,the temperature measured will be lower, that will lead to inaccurate reading.
3.Each time when you measure the temp, you should press the forehead or drill it into the ear hole for 2-3s,and then press the corresponding button until a beep that means it completes successfully to the first measurement.

Specifications:
Power: 2 x AAA Batteries
Operating Conditions: 50°F to 104°F (10°C to 40°C); ≤80%RH, non-condensing
Atmospheric Pressure: 860 hPa to 1060 hPa
Measurement Range: 32°F-212°F (0.0°C-100°C)
Measurement Resolution: 0.1°F (0.1°C)

Package List:
1 X Forehead and Ear Thermometer
1 X Portable Case
1 X User Manual

Note:
Ear test mode is only suitable for children over 3 months. Please read the included instruction manual carefully to avoid any misuse and keep it for future reference. It is normal to obtain a slight variation in temperature readings when taking temperatures from different parts of the body.

ByT. STAPLETONon December 3, 2017
Verified Purchase
We purchased this for my sister's new baby. It comes with two AAA batteries installed with a plastic thingy that prevents the drainage of the battery while it was being shipped. The box came with a tamper proof seal, also included was a pouch and easy to read/follow instructions on the box. We NEVER inserted one in our child's rear end and we want my niece to not have to go through it either. We're happy with this purchase and hope my sister and brother in-law will be happy for a long time with this thermometer as well.
